content: Endblock's bounty campaign will be temporarily paused to prepare for its other big marketing strategy with CrowdCreate.It will resume once the Endblock team gives the green light.For more detailed information, read here: https://t.me/Jcampaigns/42597[EDIT]3/6/23Endblock bounty campaign rewards for two-weeks duration will be processed and distrbuted per Endblock team's decision.Total bounty pool for two-weeks worth campaign duration is $5,000.I'll start finalizing the spreadsheet and have the rewards distributed within 1 to 2 weeks.NOTE: The Endblock bounty campaign still has chances to resume but we will have to start over again if that happens.[EDIT]3/8/23Endblock's team has decided to accept late-entry submissions for Blog posts and video campaigns.Note: *These forms will only be open for 48 hours. *Entries for blog posts and video campaigns that are created and published (meaning, uploaded, or posted) AFTER 3/6/23 will be rejected.[EDIT]3/10/23Endblock's Video and Blog post subsmission forms are now CLOSED.I will now start finalizing the spreadsheet and have the rewards distributed within 1 to 2 weeks.Take this time to check your details on the spreadsheet especially your wallet addresses. Any mistake or error on your wallet address will result in zero rewards.[EDIT]3/22/23Endblock's USDT Bounty rewards have been sent: https://bscscan.com/tx/0x76cc95ab043eae1e2b1bbd5c155a08ca43e53fdbc5f3cf4217bd6489d1cd2c54Disclaimer: I am only the Bounty Campaign Manager for this project. I am paid only to manage this bounty campaign. I will not be held responsible should the developers/project team fail to reach their stated goals/obligations to the bounty participants, investors, and everyone else. Join (on this bounty campaign), invest (on their ICO/IDO/IEO), or use their platform at your own risk.
